1. drush status - To check the details of the drupal installtion.

2. drush pm-download [ project name ] - To download the drupal project.

3. drush en [ project name ]  - To enable the module/project.

4. drush dis [ project name ] - To disable the module/project.

5. drush pm-uninstall [ project name ] - To uninstall the module/project completely .

6. drush up -n | grep available  - To check available updates.

7. drush up [name] - To upgrade only. 

8. drush upc [name] - To update the codebase and then run update.php 
			OR USE 

9. drush updatedb [name]  - To update the database update script .

10. drush up drupal - To update the drupal core . 

